{"about_the_game":"Orbital Clash is an turn-based tactical/strategic game in an austere retro graphic design.<br>Developed by a single author for his own entertainment and made available publicly.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Control and protect your HQ against aggressive aliens or a human opponent.<br></li><li>Mine resources and build your infrastructure on a procedurally generated planet system.<br></li><li>Build and dispatch your battleships and carriers into intense space battles.<br></li><li>Settle and terraform worlds with dynamic weather and terrain.<br></li><li>Dominte the system in or just try to survive for as long as possible.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game Modes</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>CLEANSING \u2013 Destroy alien infestation and secure the whole system.<br></li><li>SURVIVAL \u2013 Try to save your bare life in the waves of aggressive alien queens and their offspring. <br></li><li>COOPERATIVE and COMPETETIVE MULTIPLAYER \u2013 Play all modes either with our against another player.<br></li><li>ARCADE \u2013 Casual gameplay with simple tasks and gradually increasing difficulty.<br></li><li>TUTORIAL and BEGINNER mode \u2013 Helps to overcome seemingly complicated controls and steep learning curve.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game mechanics</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>TURN-BASED strategy \u2013 Set up the movement of units, attack with weapons, build and manage your infrastructure and defences.<br></li><li>PROPULSION movement \u2013 Spaceships move along trajectories with gradual acceleration and braking. Don't overshoot your destination.<br></li><li>TERRAFORMATION\u2013 Dynamic planet environment with the possibility of terraforming to improve your situation or to make your's opponent's life much worse.<br></li><li>MAP and GAME LOGS \u2013 Keep the situational awareness with a minimap and detailed log of game events.<br></li><li>Optional FOG OF WAR \u2013 Search fo enemy spaceships or alien entities.</li></ul>","